    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at the stars tonight and it just hit me how much of a mistake it is to even be here. just a bunch of atoms accidentally bumping into each other in a void that doesn't care. there's nothing after this, no meaning, no purpose. just eventually everything goes cold and dark. it feels like there's really no point in fighting it.",
